      ## HTTP Request Headers

      `GET get something /this-is-a-param`{:.param.http}

      `POST post something http://example.org/test`{:.param.http}

      `DELETE delete something http://something-else`{:.param.http}

      `PUT put something http://something-else`{:.param.http}
      
      ## Request Parameters

      | Parameter           | Description
      | -------------       | -------------
      | `name`{:.param}     | Username. Between 3 and 32 characters. Allowed: alphanumeric, “x”, “-“ and “_”. Must start with a letter.
      | `email`{:.param}    | User email. Between 5 and 255 characters.
      | `fullName`{:.param} | User full name. Between 5 and 64 characters.
      | `password`{:.param} | User password. Between 6 and 64 characters.

